{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482823995,"sessionID":"ses_314328759ffeSwO8I1laVGgGu4","part":{"id":"prt_cebcfe582001y3FhLzCQ4CdXtb","sessionID":"ses_314328759ffeSwO8I1laVGgGu4","messageID":"msg_cebcfd4eb001BLzRb7mlhLADV3","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nImplement a \"wishlist promote\" feature that allows users to promote wishlist items to errands (E key) or genesis quests (G key) from a new TUI view. After promotion, optionally delete the wishlist item. Wire callbacks through the `tui.ts` main loop.\n\n## Instructions\n\n- **Branch:** `feature/wishlist-promote` on `main`\n- Use conventional commits with scope `wishlist-promote`\n- Commit after each logical unit of work (not squashed)\n- Do NOT push to remote\n- Do NOT modify `tasks/` directory\n- Use `bun dev` for testing, never the global binary\n- Run `bun run build` to verify at the end\n- Follow existing codebase patterns (Bun runtime, ESM, TypeScript strict, neo-blessed TUI)\n\n## Discoveries\n\n1. **Wishlist store** (`src/lib/wishlist-store.ts`) already has full CRUD: `loadWishlist()`, `addItem()`, `deleteItem()`, `listItems()`. Items have `id`, `text`, `created_at`, `tags` fields.\n\n2. **TUI architecture** follows a pattern where each view is a class with a blessed screen (QuestPicker, TaskBrowser, PlanReview, GenesisReview). They are wired together via Promise-based wrappers in `src/commands/tui.ts` which runs the main loop.\n\n3. **The main loop** (`cmdTui()` in `src/commands/tui.ts`) cycles: Quest Picker → Task Browser → Launch → Monitor → back. Actions from quest picker include `select`, `plan`, `genesis`, `errand`, `quit`.\n\n4. **Errand flow** (`handleErrandFlow`) prompts user for a description via readline, runs `runErrandPlanner()`, shows plan review. **Genesis flow** (`handleGenesisFlow`) prompts for a vision, runs `runGenesisPlanner()`, shows genesis review.\n\n5. **Quest Picker** already has E (errand) and G (genesis) keys. The wishlist view needs a W key on the quest picker to navigate to it, and then E/G keys within the wishlist view to promote items.\n\n6. **`QuestPickerAction`** type in `tui-quest-picker.ts` defines the possible actions. It currently has: `select`, `plan`, `genesis`, `errand`, `quit`. Needs a new `wishlist` action type.\n\n## Accomplished\n\n### Completed:\n1. **Modified `handleErrandFlow`** in `src/commands/tui.ts` to accept an optional `prefill?: string` parameter. When provided, it skips the readline prompt and uses the pre-filled text directly.\n2. **Modified `handleGenesisFlow`** in `src/commands/tui.ts` to accept an optional `prefill?: string` parameter. Same skip-prompt behavior.\n3. **Created `src/lib/tui-wishlist.ts`** — A full `WishlistPicker` class following the same blessed TUI pattern as QuestPicker. Has E (errand), G (genesis), D (delete), Esc (back), Q (quit) keybindings. Shows items in a list with detail pane.\n\n### Still needs to be done:\n1. **Wire wishlist into `tui.ts` main loop** — Add W key handling in `cmdTui()` to navigate to the wishlist picker, handle `promote-errand` and `promote-genesis` actions from wishlist by calling `handleErrandFlow`/`handleGenesisFlow` with pre-filled text.\n2. **Add W key to QuestPicker** — Add `wishlist` action type to `QuestPickerAction`, add `onWishlist` callback to `QuestPickerOptions`, bind W key in the picker, add W to status bar keybind hints.\n3. **Post-promotion deletion** — After errand/genesis flow completes (from wishlist promotion), ask the user if they want to delete the wishlist item. This should happen back in the `cmdTui()` main loop after the flow returns.\n4. **Run `bun run build`** to verify everything compiles.\n5. **Commit** each logical unit of work.\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n- **`src/commands/tui.ts`** — Main TUI loop orchestrator. MODIFIED: `handleErrandFlow` and `handleGenesisFlow` now accept optional `prefill` parameter. Still needs: wiring wishlist view into main loop, post-promotion delete prompt.\n- **`src/lib/tui-wishlist.ts`** — CREATED: New `WishlistPicker` class with blessed TUI view for browsing and promoting wishlist items.\n- **`src/lib/tui-quest-picker.ts`** — Quest picker view. NEEDS MODIFICATION: Add `wishlist` to `QuestPickerAction` type, add `onWishlist` callback, bind W key, update status bar.\n- **`src/lib/wishlist-store.ts`** — READ ONLY: Existing wishlist CRUD (loadWishlist, addItem, deleteItem, listItems, WishlistItem type).\n- **`src/lib/tui-browser.ts`** — READ ONLY: Task browser view (reference for patterns).\n- **`src/lib/tui.ts`** — READ ONLY: Wave monitor TUI (WomboTUI class, reference for patterns).\n- **`src/lib/tui-session.ts`** — READ ONLY: TUI session persistence.\n- **`src/lib/errand-planner.ts`** — READ ONLY: Errand planner (runErrandPlanner, applyErrandPlan).\n- **`src/lib/genesis-planner.ts`** — READ ONLY: Genesis planner (runGenesisPlanner).\n- **`AGENTS.md`** — READ ONLY: Development guidelines.","time":{"start":1773482823994,"end":1773482823994}}}
