{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773482832711,"sessionID":"ses_314328759ffeSwO8I1laVGgGu4","part":{"id":"prt_cebd071b5002XRkKrJ5ZPj7SRo","sessionID":"ses_314328759ffeSwO8I1laVGgGu4","messageID":"msg_cebd0662800175JfhqiXGcmJ8E","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01S4Lptwb85NYqFac63eHn7P","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git log --oneline -10","description":"Check recent git commits"},"output":"f1ba6ae refactor(tasks): flatten chains for maximum wave parallelism\nb3729da Merge branch 'feature/token-parse' into main\ncdb6b6b feat(token-parse): integrate TokenCollector into ProcessMonitor\nb0085eb Merge branch 'feature/wave-detach-audit' into main\na23f37e fix(wave-detach-audit): mark resolving_conflict agents as interrupted on quit\n49a1c4c docs(wave-detach-audit): document resume.ts recovery lifecycle\n677867e docs(wave-detach-audit): document agent process lifecycle findings\na15077a feat(token-parse): add UsageRecord type, TokenCollector class, and update OpenCodeEvent tokens shape\n77b230b Merge branch 'feature/wishlist-store' into main\n202c7d0 Merge branch 'feature/tui-sort-keybind' into main\n","title":"Check recent git commits","metadata":{"output":"f1ba6ae refactor(tasks): flatten chains for maximum wave parallelism\nb3729da Merge branch 'feature/token-parse' into main\ncdb6b6b feat(token-parse): integrate TokenCollector into ProcessMonitor\nb0085eb Merge branch 'feature/wave-detach-audit' into main\na23f37e fix(wave-detach-audit): mark resolving_conflict agents as interrupted on quit\n49a1c4c docs(wave-detach-audit): document resume.ts recovery lifecycle\n677867e docs(wave-detach-audit): document agent process lifecycle findings\na15077a feat(token-parse): add UsageRecord type, TokenCollector class, and update OpenCodeEvent tokens shape\n77b230b Merge branch 'feature/wishlist-store' into main\n202c7d0 Merge branch 'feature/tui-sort-keybind' into main\n","exit":0,"description":"Check recent git commits","truncated":false},"time":{